					About


		Howard Bancorp, Inc. is the bank holding company of Howard Bank. The Company's primary business is to own all of the capital stock of Howard Bank. The Company operates through Community Banking segment. Howard Bank is a trust company, which has approximately four operating subsidiaries. The Company offers a range of services to... (more)





