 and online banking services. It also provides a variety of loans that includes home equity, real estate, commercial construction, installment and overdraft line of credit. The bank offers night depository, wire transfer, cash management and merchant services. In addition, it provides various investment options that include business succession and executive compensation plans. The bank s personal investment services include risk protection and planned giving. Howard Bank offers business lending and online banking and bill payment services. Additionally, the bank provides public servant and sustainability loan programs.... Read more LessMessage from {{profile.name}}... Read more LessProvided by CitySearchThis business is a Superpages advertiser.SocialCategories{{c.name}}, {{c.name}}, Additional Contacts{{phone}}Alt{{phone}}Fax{{phone}}FreeIn Business Since2005... More2005 LessWebsiteView Menu More DetailsThe person icon  Employee Image indicates that the reviewer is an employee of Dex Media, Inc. Dex Media operates and sells advertising on Superpages.com. The views expressed in reviews are the opinion of each respective reviewer and do not necessarily reflect the view of Dex Media.Data provided by one or more of the following: Dex Media, Acxiom, Infogroup, Yext, Pingup.



