                                                Howard Bancorp Inc
                                             Company Snapshot
                                            









                                            
	Howard Bancorp Inc operates in the State commercial banks sector.
	
	In addition to historical fundamental analyses, the complete report available to purchase compares Howard Bancorp Inc with three other
	
			companies in this sector in the United States:
		
	ACNB Corporation
	
		(2016
	sales of $53.26 million
		of which 85%
		was Banking),
	
	Colony Bankcorp, Inc.
	
		($54.14 million
		), and
	
	Peoples Bancorp of North Carolina, Inc.
	
		($53.79 million
		of which 100%
		was Banking & Related Activities).
	
	Sales Analysis. 
	Howard Bancorp Inc reported sales of $53.61 million
		for the
		
		year ending
		December of 2016.
	
		This
		
			represents
		
				an
			
			increase of 18.4%
		
		 versus 2015, when the company's sales were $45.28 million.
	
			Sales at Howard Bancorp Inc have increased during each of the previous five years
		
		(and since 2011, sales have increased a total of 240%).
	

	




 


 
 


 
 


 
 











 



 













 










